From: enfs-dkms
Subject: [PATCH] net/sunrpc/Makefile: link sunrpc_enfs_adapter.o into sunrpc.ko

When CONFIG_SUNRPC_ENFS is set, link sunrpc_enfs_adapter.o (which
provides the rpc_multipath_ops_* registry that enfs.ko uses) into
sunrpc.ko.

The sunrpc_enfs_adapter.c file is dropped into net/sunrpc/ at
src-tree-build time by scripts/build-src-tree.sh.

---
 net/sunrpc/Makefile | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

--- a/net/sunrpc/Makefile
+++ b/net/sunrpc/Makefile
@@ -19,3 +19,4 @@ sunrpc-$(CONFIG_SUNRPC_DEBUG) += debugfs.o
 sunrpc-$(CONFIG_SUNRPC_BACKCHANNEL) += backchannel_rqst.o
 sunrpc-$(CONFIG_PROC_FS) += stats.o
 sunrpc-$(CONFIG_SYSCTL) += sysctl.o
+sunrpc-$(CONFIG_SUNRPC_ENFS) += sunrpc_enfs_adapter.o
